{"tid":1192313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：曾偉雄是港人參與國家治理好例子","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T12:37:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"00d778f01d5f60e868ce00a473111ae8e6848163","tid":1192313,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CY-SPEECH-190608-14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCY-SPEECH-190608-14.jpg&h=14146ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】前警務處處長曾偉雄獲委任為國家禁毒委員會副主任，並獲中央提名競逐聯合國職位，全國政協副主席兼前特首梁振英形容，曾偉雄是港人參與國家治理活生生的例子。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英在社交網站指出投擲汽油彈案不尋常，又指有人為政治利益激化青年，梁振英被追問是否認為案件是否涉及政治利益，他沒有回應。"},{"pid":"fc8fa6f4037c57a6ae2c4d6305ee8cba9496fb49","tid":1192313,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:07:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350946&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=e233a5af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350946&h=23c2a15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350946</a>"},{"pid":"0b7736ff0f471b8dad84abcd18f7d85a20da4dfa","tid":1192313,"uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"狼狽為奸都係好事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1964c6dc3684c3e802b33e8895fce88e0bbaf73c","tid":1192313,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"共人用共狗"},{"pid":"9c7357a9294a82ca90e5601505dc0b59db08f54e","tid":1192313,"uid":4420,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTi